---
// Landing sections — custom Astro components with Starwind-inspired card, pill, and CTA patterns.
---

<section class="promo-flow" aria-label="Smart Caregiver landing sections">
    <div class="promo-inner">
        <section class="proof-strip" aria-label="Keunggulan utama">
            <article>
                <strong>01</strong>
                <span>Pengingat rawat harian yang mudah diikuti keluarga.</span>
            </article>
            <article>
                <strong>02</strong>
                <span>Panduan perawatan lansia dibuat ringkas dan praktis.</span>
            </article>
            <article>
                <strong>03</strong>
                <span>Didukung insight publik dari data kesehatan lansia.</span>
            </article>
        </section>

        <section id="cara-kerja" class="feature-band section-pad">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <span class="eyebrow">Cara kerja</span>
                <h2>Satu tempat untuk membuat rutinitas merawat terasa lebih ringan.</h2>
                <p>
                    Smart Caregiver membantu keluarga menyusun jadwal, memahami
                    kebutuhan lansia, dan melihat prioritas perawatan tanpa harus
                    membuka banyak catatan terpisah.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-grid">
                <article class="feature-card featured">
                    <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
                    <h3>Atur agenda rawat</h3>
                    <p>
                        Jadwalkan obat, aktivitas, kontrol, hidrasi, dan catatan
                        penting agar pendamping tidak melewatkan hal kecil.
                    </p>
                </article>
                <article class="feature-card">
                    <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">♡</span>
                    <h3>Pahami kondisi harian</h3>
                    <p>
                        Simpan catatan sederhana tentang mood, keluhan, dan
                        aktivitas agar keluarga punya konteks yang sama.
                    </p>
                </article>
                <article class="feature-card">
                    <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
                    <h3>Lihat insight publik</h3>
                    <p>
                        Dashboard data memberi gambaran tren kesehatan lansia,
                        percakapan digital, dan topik yang sering dicari.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="preview-band section-pad" aria-labelledby="preview-title">
            <div class="phone-card" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="phone-topline"></div>
                <div class="care-row active">
                    <span>08.00</span>
                    <strong>Obat pagi</strong>
                    <small>Selesai</small>
                </div>
                <div class="care-row">
                    <span>10.30</span>
                    <strong>Senam ringan</strong>
                    <small>15 menit</small>
                </div>
                <div class="care-row">
                    <span>14.00</span>
                    <strong>Cek tekanan darah</strong>
                    <small>Pengingat</small>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-note">
                    <strong>Catatan hari ini</strong>
                    <p>Nafsu makan baik, tidur siang 40 menit, perlu minum lebih banyak.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="preview-copy">
                <span class="eyebrow">Untuk keluarga</span>
                <h2 id="preview-title">Promosi aplikasi yang tetap terasa hangat, bukan terlalu teknis.</h2>
                <p>
                    Landing page ini menjaga visual yang sudah ada: bersih, cerah,
                    dan ramah. Komponen dibuat custom agar tidak terasa template,
                    dengan pola kartu dan pill ala Starwind/shadcn sebagai referensi.
                </p>
                <a class="text-link" href="/public-dashboard">Lihat dashboard data →</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="unduh" class="download-band section-pad" aria-labelledby="download-title">
            <div>
                <span class="eyebrow light">Unduh aplikasi</span>
                <h2 id="download-title">Mulai dampingi orang tersayang dengan lebih tenang.</h2>
                <p>
                    Siapkan rutinitas rawat, bagikan catatan ke keluarga, dan gunakan
                    insight kesehatan lansia sebagai bahan memahami kebutuhan harian.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="download-actions">
                <a class="store-button" href="#" aria-label="Unduh Smart Caregiver di Google Play">
                    <small>Segera hadir di</small>
                    <strong>Google Play</strong>
                </a>
                <a class="store-button secondary" href="#" aria-label="Unduh Smart Caregiver di App Store">
                    <small>Segera hadir di</small>
                    <strong>App Store</strong>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .promo-flow {
        width: 100vw;
        margin: 0 calc(50% - 50vw);
        background:
            linear-gradient(180deg, var(--canvas) 0%, var(--blue-soft) 44%, var(--canvas) 100%);
    }

    .promo-inner {
        width: min(100% - 48px, 1180px);
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-pad {
        padding: clamp(72px, 9vw, 120px) 0;
    }

    .proof-strip {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 14px;
        padding: 24px 0 0;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    .proof-strip article {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 96px;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 12%, var(--hairline));
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--canvas) 88%, transparent);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 48px color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 10%, transparent);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .proof-strip strong {
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-full);
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--on-dark);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .proof-strip span {
        color: var(--body-strong);
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .section-heading {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        width: fit-content;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        padding: 7px 14px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 10%, var(--canvas));
        color: var(--blue);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .eyebrow.light {
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--canvas) 12%, transparent);
        color: var(--on-dark);
    }

    .section-heading h2,
    .preview-copy h2,
    .download-band h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.15rem, 4.4vw, 4.8rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.055em;
        line-height: 0.98;
    }

    .section-heading p,
    .preview-copy p,
    .download-band p {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin-top: 18px;
        color: var(--body);
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.25vw, 1.16rem);
    }

    .feature-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 18px;
    }

    .feature-card {
        min-height: 300px;
        padding: 28px;
        border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
        border-radius: 30px;
        background: var(--surface-card);
        transition:
            transform 180ms ease,
            border-color 180ms ease,
            box-shadow 180ms ease;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 26%, var(--hairline));
        box-shadow: 0 20px 42px color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 10%, transparent);
    }

    .feature-card.featured {
        background:
            radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-yellow) 34%, transparent), transparent 30%),
            var(--ink);
        color: var(--on-dark);
    }

    .feature-card.featured h3,
    .feature-card.featured p {
        color: var(--on-dark);
    }

    .card-icon {
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 64px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-full);
        background: var(--blue-soft);
        color: var(--blue);
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .featured .card-icon {
        background: var(--blue);
        color: var(--on-primary);
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .feature-card p {
        color: var(--body);
    }

    .preview-band {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(300px, 0.82fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: clamp(28px, 6vw, 88px);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .phone-card {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
        width: min(100%, 430px);
        padding: 28px;
        border: 10px solid var(--ink);
        border-radius: 44px;
        background: var(--canvas);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 70px color-mix(in srgb, var(--ink) 18%, transparent);
    }

    .phone-card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        right: -28px;
        bottom: 64px;
        width: 98px;
        height: 98px;
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: var(--accent-yellow);
        box-shadow: -20px 22px 0 var(--blue);
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .phone-topline {
        width: 88px;
        height: 6px;
        margin: 0 auto 12px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        background: var(--hairline);
    }

    .care-row,
    .mini-note {
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: var(--surface-soft);
    }

    .care-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .care-row.active {
        background: var(--blue);
        color: var(--on-primary);
    }

    .care-row span,
    .care-row small {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .care-row strong,
    .mini-note strong {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .mini-note p {
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: var(--body);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .text-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin-top: 24px;
        color: var(--blue);
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .download-band {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
        gap: 36px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 64px;
        padding-inline: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px);
        border-radius: 40px;
        background:
            radial-gradient(circle at 86% 28%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 44%, transparent), transparent 28%),
            var(--ink);
        color: var(--on-dark);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .download-band h2,
    .download-band p {
        color: var(--on-dark);
    }

    .download-band p {
        color: var(--on-dark-soft);
    }

    .download-actions {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
        min-width: 240px;
    }

    .store-button {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2px;
        padding: 16px 22px;
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: var(--on-dark);
        color: var(--ink);
    }

    .store-button.secondary {
        border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--on-dark) 18%, transparent);
        background: var(--surface-dark-elevated);
        color: var(--on-dark);
    }

    .store-button small {
        color: inherit;
        opacity: 0.64;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .store-button strong {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 1.16rem;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .proof-strip,
        .feature-grid,
        .preview-band,
        .download-band {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .proof-strip {
            transform: none;
            padding-top: 24px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            min-height: 0;
        }

        .card-icon {
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        .phone-card {
            justify-self: center;
        }

        .download-actions {
            min-width: 0;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .promo-inner {
            width: min(100% - 32px, 520px);
        }

        .proof-strip article {
            min-height: 0;
        }

        .phone-card::after {
            display: none;
        }

        .download-band {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }
    }
</style>
